Manifestor.description: Initiators and impact makers, known for their ability to start projects and make things happen.
Manifestor.strategy: Informing others before taking action to avoid resistance.
challenges: Resistance from others if not informing

Generator.description: The builders and doers, characterized by their sustainable life force energy.
Generator.strategy: Responding to situations and opportunities, rather than initiating.
challenges: Frustration from not waiting to respond
Burnout if not aligned with true work

Projector.description: Guides and directors, skilled in understanding others and managing energies.
Projector.strategy: Waiting for recognition and invitation to maximize their impact.

Reflector.description: Reflectors are rare and unique, mirroring the health and wellbeing of their environment.
Reflector.strategy: Waiting a full lunar cycle before making major decisions.
